:"和理非要出黎抗衡藍絲喇"},{"pid":"70c3216fe253c432048ce78bdca4a1bd62580ffe","tid":1728911,"uid":98431,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:27:27.000Z","msg":"對家用呢招係想將手足拖入泥漿摔角 引手足主動上去守城 畫面愈難睇 對家愈開心<br />\n<br />\n醉翁之意極其明顯 其實對家要攻 根本有好多時機可以攻入去 例如係凌晨 例如係實彈<br />\n只係上星期中大一戰做得太難睇 加上又已經引起左國際關注 唔可以明攻"},{"pid":"1a492e255bb1f973e46d48eedb7bafc441768360","tid":1728911,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:27:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"784bb16a8f942cdff697cf37e83c710105777691","tid":1728911,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:27:54.000Z","msg":"參考佔中一戰 旺角金鐘 唇寒齒亡 相繼失守<br />\n<br />\n當初守城一戰係呼應中大開花<br />\n而家中大手足都退左 其他大學手足請盡快撤離<span style=\"color: red;\"> 保住自由之身先有花開結果一日</span><br />\n<br />\n唔好跟機 繼續快閃<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人會話 咩都唔好守 幾時連你自己屋企都唔守 俾人入去?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">問題係你連今日都捱唔過 聽朝癲狗入你屋 連門都唔洗開</span><br />\n<br />\n我明大家憂心既地方 問題係可唔可以睇多兩步 權衡得失"},{"pid":"00048fb1f504c26f7a4f2768ccfeeca074689781","tid":1728911,"uid":104165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0826ae39b7ffffd79f319566696ddfc1e904fb15","tid":1728911,"uid":69215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:28:05.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"edeb5ee0f60e33cc123c203e71d161ac79ac352f","tid":1728911,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4944439b89710344383086d2baa641bd5149b409","tid":1728911,"uid":69215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:21:41.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:28:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41eb9381840457e91f37